专访金银潭医院上海医疗队周新：“新冠肺炎”重症患者救治难度比SARS和禽流感大。
Interview with Zhou Xinxin of Shanghai Medical Team of Gold and Silver Pool Hospital: SARS was more difficult to treat than SARS and avian influenza.
